'''膀胱'''（urinary bladder，bladder），文言'''{{zy|脬|pāo|ㄆㄠ}}'''，方言'''{{Zy|尿|suī|ㄙㄨㄟ}}脬'''、'''{{Zy|尿|suī|ㄙㄨㄟ}}{{zy|泡|pāo|ㄆㄠ}}'''，是动物用于贮[[尿|尿]]的中空肌性囊状器官，在排尿前储存[[腎|肾脏]]产生的尿液。人类的膀胱位于[[骨盆|骨盆]]底部。尿液通过[[输尿管|输尿管]]进入膀胱，然后经[[尿道|尿道]]排出。正常成年人的膀胱容量平均为350－500毫升，最大容量为800毫升。<ref>{{cite book|last1=Boron|first1=Walter F.|last2=Boulpaep|first2=Emile L.|title=Medical Physiology|date=2016|publisher=Elsevier Health Sciences|location=3|isbn=9781455733286|page=738|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=6QzhCwAAQBAJ&pg=PA738|access-date=2016-06-01|archive-date=2019-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191217034444/https://books.google.com/books?id=6QzhCwAAQBAJ&pg=PA738|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Walker-Smith|first1=John|last2=Murch|first2=Simon|editor1-last=Cardozo|editor1-first=Linda|title=Diseases of the Small Intestine in Childhood|date=1999|publisher=CRC Press|isbn=9781901865059|page=16|edition=4|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=EMMUyiKOOiEC&pg=PA16|access-date=2016-06-01|archive-date=2019-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191217034443/https://books.google.com/books?id=EMMUyiKOOiEC&pg=PA16|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":7">{{Cite book|title=系统解剖学|last=丁|first=文龙|publisher=人民卫生出版社|year=2018|isbn=9787117267182|location=北京|pages=149|last2=刘|first2=学政}}</ref>

== 结构 ==
人类的膀胱是位于[[骨盆|骨盆]]底部的中空肌性器官。在[[解剖学|解剖学]]上，膀胱可分为尖、体、底和颈四部。<ref name=":7" />膀胱尖朝向[[恥骨聯合|耻骨联合]]上部，由此沿腹前壁至脐之间有{{Translink|en|median umbilical ligament|脐正中韧带}}。腹膜由膀胱尖延伸至腹壁，形成{{Translink|en|middle umbilical fold|脐正中襞}}。膀胱的后面朝向后下方，呈三角形，称为膀胱底。膀胱的最下部称为膀胱颈，包围通向[[尿道|尿道]]的尿道内口。男性的膀胱颈与[[前列腺|前列腺]]毗邻，女性的膀胱颈与[[盆膈|盆膈]]相邻。<ref name=":0">{{cite book|last1=Netter|first1=Frank H.|title=Atlas of Human Anatomy Including Student Consult Interactive Ancillaries and Guides|date=2014|publisher=W B Saunders Co|location=Philadelphia, Penn.|isbn=978-14557-0418-7|pages=346–8|edition=6th}}</ref>女性膀胱的最大容量低于男性。<ref name=":14" />

膀胱有三个开口，分别为左、右输尿管口和尿道内口。两条输尿管经输尿管口进入膀胱。输尿管开口处有粘膜瓣，可起到防止尿液回流进入输尿管而发生[[膀胱输尿管返流|膀胱输尿管返流]]的作用。<ref>{{cite web|title=SEER Training:Urinary Bladder|url=https://training.seer.cancer.gov/anatomy/urinary/components/bladder.html|website=training.seer.cancer.gov|language=en|access-date=2021-07-18|archive-date=2017-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222101654/https://training.seer.cancer.gov/anatomy/urinary/components/bladder.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>两输尿管口之间的皱襞称为输尿管间襞<ref name=":0" />。膀胱底内面有一呈三角形的区域，位于两输尿管口与尿道内口之间，称为{{Tsl|en|trigone of the bladder|膀胱三角}}。此处的膀胱[[黏膜|黏膜]]始终保持平滑，以便尿液流出。<ref name=":5">{{cite journal|title=The development of the bladder trigone, the center of the anti-reflux mechanism|author=|date=2007-10|journal=Development|issue=20|doi=10.1242/dev.011270|volume=134|pages=3763–9|pmid=17881488|vauthors=Viana R, Batourina E, Huang H, Dressler GR, Kobayashi A, Behringer RR, Shapiro E, Hensle T, Lambert S, Mendelsohn C|doi-access=free}}</ref>

膀胱壁收缩时，膀胱内面的黏膜聚集成皱襞，称为{{Tsl|en|rugae|膀胱襞}}。膀胱壁的肌层为[[逼尿肌|逼尿肌]]，由[[平滑肌|平滑肌]]纤维以螺旋、纵向和环形三种方式排列而成。<ref name=":2">{{cite book|last1=Young|first1=Barbara|last2=O'Dowd|first2=Geraldine|last3=Woodford|first3=Phillip|title=Wheater's functional histology: a text and colour atlas.|publisher=Elsevier|location=Philadelphia|date=2013|isbn=9780702047473|edition=6th|chapter=Urinary system|pages=315–7}}</ref>逼尿肌收缩时可促进[[排尿|排尿]]，膀胱充盈时逼尿肌保持舒张。<ref name=":9">{{cite journal|title=Urinary bladder contraction and relaxation: physiology and pathophysiology|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_physiological-reviews_2004-07_84_3/page/935|author=|date=2004-07|journal=Physiol. Rev.|issue=3|doi=10.1152/physrev.00038.2003|volume=84|pages=935–86|pmid=15269341|vauthors=Andersson KE, Arner A}}</ref>膀胱壁的厚度通常为3－5毫米，充盈良好时厚度通常小于3毫米。<ref name=":1">{{cite book|title=Imaging and Urodynamics of the Lower Urinary Tract|author=Uday Patel|publisher=Springer Science & Business Media|year=2010|isbn=9781848828360}}[https://books.google.com/books?id=Z4t3dnDR1e8C&pg=PA12 第12页] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Z4t3dnDR1e8C&pg=PA12 |date=20210415032312 }}</ref>
<gallery>
File:Gray1140.png|膀胱结构图
File:Male and female bladder.svg|男性、女性膀胱位置
</gallery>

=== 毗邻 ===
男性的前列腺位于尿道口外侧，此处的膀胱组织受前列腺中叶推挤形成隆起，称为[[膀胱垂|膀胱垂]]。当前列腺增生时，这一隆起将会扩大。<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":7" />

膀胱位于腹膜腔以下。男性的膀胱位于[[直肠|直肠]]前方，与直肠由{{Translink|en|recto-vesical pouch|直肠膀胱陷凹}}相隔，由{{Translink|en|levator ani|肛提肌}}与前列腺的[[结缔组织|结缔组织]]支撑；女性的膀胱位于子宫、阴道前方，与子宫由{{Translink|en|vesico-uterine pouch|膀胱子宫陷凹}}相隔，由肛提肌与[[阴道|阴道]]的上部支撑。<ref name=":1" />

=== 血液供应与淋巴引流 ===
动脉血液经{{Translink|en|internal iliac arteries|髂内动脉}}进入[[膀胱上动脉|膀胱上]]、[[膀胱下动脉|下动脉]]，分别向膀胱的上、下部供血。在女性体内，子宫动脉和阴道动脉亦可向膀胱供血。膀胱的静脉引流开始于膀胱下侧表面的[[微血管|毛细血管网]]，静脉血汇入膀胱静脉丛，之后流入{{Translink|en|internal iliac veins|髂内静脉}}。<ref name=":3" />

由膀胱产生的[[淋巴液|淋巴液]]进入位于膀胱粘膜层、肌层和浆膜层的[[毛细淋巴管|毛细淋巴管]]网，然后汇入三组淋巴管，一组在膀胱底部靠近膀胱三角处排出；一组从膀胱顶部排出；另一组从膀胱外表面下部排出。这些淋巴管大部分汇入{{Translink|en|external iliac lymph nodes|髂外淋巴结}}。<ref name=":3">{{Cite book|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/920806541|title=Gray's anatomy : the anatomical basis of clinical practice|year=2016|isbn=9780702052309|editor=Standring, Susan|edition=41st|location=Philadelphia|pages=1255–1261|section=Urinary bladder|oclc=920806541|access-date=2021-07-18|archive-date=2020-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200614122111/https://www.worldcat.org/title/grays-anatomy-the-anatomical-basis-of-clinical-practice/oclc/920806541|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 神经支配 ===
膀胱接受[[交感神经|交感神经]]与[[副交感神经|副交感神经]]的支配，实现器官的感觉与运动功能。<ref name=":3" />其[[运动神经元|运动性神经]]纤维来自{{Translink|en|superior hypogastric plexuses|上腹下丛|上}}、{{Translink|en|inferior hypogastric plexuses|下腹下丛}}的交感神经与{{Translink|en|pelvic splanchnic nerves|盆内脏神经}}的副交感神经。<ref name=":4">{{cite book|last=Moore|first=Keith|title=Essential Clinical Anatomy, Third Edition|year=2007|publisher=Lippincott Williams & Wilkins|isbn=978-0-7817-6274-8|pages=227–228|author2=Anne Agur}}</ref>

[[感染|感染]]、[[结石|结石]]造成的牵张或炎症可刺激膀胱产生神经兴奋，信号主要通过副交感神经传导。<ref name=":3" />信号到达{{Translink|en|sacral nerves|骶神经}}S<sub>2</sub>－S<sub>4</sub><ref name=":6">{{Cite book|title=Ganong's review of medical physiology|first1=Kim E|last1=Barrett|first2=Susan M|last2=Barman|first3=Jason X-J|last3=Yuan|first4=Heddwen|last4=Brooks|isbn=9781260122404|edition=26th|location=New York|oclc=1076268769|year=2019|chapter=37. Renal function & Micturition: The Bladder|pages=681–682}}</ref>后通过[[脊髓|脊髓]]背柱传导至大脑<ref name=":4" />。

=== 组织学结构 ===
{{Multiple image|
image1=Gray1141.png|caption1=膀胱壁结构
|image2=2605 The Bladder zh.jpg|caption2=男性膀胱，可见变移上皮、部分膀胱壁|direction=vertical}}

在显微镜下观察，可见膀胱结构分为黏膜、肌层与外膜。<ref name=":2" />

膀胱上皮被为{{Translink|en|urothelium|尿路上皮}}，是一种由三到六层细胞构成的[[變移上皮|变移上皮]]。<ref name=":2" />细胞表面有一层含[[糖萼|糖萼]]的黏膜，可保护细胞免受尿液侵蚀。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Histamine modulation of urinary bladder urothelium, lamina propria and detrusor contractile activity via H1 and H2 receptors.|author=|first1=Z|last2=Chess-Williams|first2=R|date=2019-03-07|journal=Scientific Reports|issue=1|doi=10.1038/s41598-019-40384-1|volume=9|pages=3899|bibcode=2019NatSR...9.3899S|pmc=6405771|pmid=30846750|last3=Moro|first3=C|last1=Stromberga}}</ref>上皮细胞位于[[基底膜|基底膜]]与{{Translink|en|lamina propria|固有层}}之上。黏膜还构成了尿路上皮血－尿屏障，可避免感染。<ref>{{cite journal|title=The distribution and function of chondroitin sulfate and other sulfated glycosaminoglycans in the human bladder and their contribution to the protective bladder barrier.|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-urology_2013-01_189_1/page/336|first1=DA|date=January 2013|journal=The Journal of Urology|issue=1|doi=10.1016/j.juro.2012.09.022|volume=189|pages=336–42|pmid=23174248|last1=Janssen}}</ref>

肉眼下可见肌层由内纵行、中环形和外纵行三层平滑肌纤维构成，它们共同构成逼尿肌。<ref name=":2" />

膀胱顶部的外膜为{{tsl|en|serosa|漿膜 (組織學)|漿膜}}，其余处多为[[疏鬆結締組織|疏松结缔组织]]。<ref name=":8">{{Cite book|title=组织学与胚胎学|last=李|first=继承|publisher=人民卫生出版社|year=2018|isbn=9787117266383|location=北京|pages=172|last2=曾|first2=园山}}</ref><ref name=":2" /><ref>{{cite journal|title=The Role of the Mucosa in Normal and Abnormal Bladder Function.|first1=CH|last2=Vahabi|first2=B|date=October 2016|journal=Basic & Clinical Pharmacology & Toxicology|doi=10.1111/bcpt.12626|volume=119 Suppl 3|pages=57–62|pmc=5555362|pmid=27228303|last1=Fry}}</ref>

=== 发育 ===
发育中胚胎的后端有一泄殖腔。胚胎发育的第四周到第七周，泄殖腔分隔为腹侧的[[尿生殖窦|尿生殖窦]]和背侧的原始直肠。两腔之间形成的壁称为{{Translink|en|urorectal septum|尿直肠隔}}。<ref name=":8" />尿生殖窦分为三段，上部最大，发育为膀胱，中部成为尿道，下部则根据胚胎的生物性别而变化。<ref>{{cite book|last1=Sadley|first1=TW|title=Langman's medical embryology|date=2019|location=Philadelphia|publisher=Wolters Kluwer|isbn=9781496383907|edition=14th|section=Bladder and urethra|pages=263–66}}</ref>

人类膀胱起源于尿生殖窦，最初与{{Translink|en|allantois|尿囊}}相延续。膀胱的上部与下部独立发育，在发育中期互相连接。此时输尿管从{{Translink|en|mesonephric ducts|中肾管}}移至膀胱三角。<ref name=":5" />婴幼儿的膀胱位于[[腹腔|腹腔]]。<ref name=":14">{{cite book|author1=Moore, Keith L.|author2=Dalley, Arthur F|title=Clinically Oriented Anatomy|url=https://archive.org/details/clinicallyorient00moor_1|edition=5th|year=2006|publisher=Lippincott Williams & Wilkins}}</ref>

== 功能 ==
{{参见|排尿}}
由[[腎|肾]]产生的尿液，在排尿前因两侧输尿管的引流聚集在膀胱中。<ref name=":6" />尿液通过尿道离开膀胱。尿道是单一的肌性管道，末端有[[尿道口|尿道口]]，尿液在尿道口离开机体。<ref name=":3" />排尿涉及肌肉的协调运动，其中包含脊髓[[反射_(生理学)|反射]]，亦受大脑、[[橋腦|脑桥]]的排尿中枢<ref>{{cite book|last1=Purves|first1=Dale|title=Neuroscience|date=2011|publisher=Sinauer|location=Sunderland, Mass.|isbn=978-0-87893-695-3|page=471|edition=5.}}</ref>等高级中枢调控。在排尿过程中，逼尿肌收缩，尿道外括约肌和会阴肌舒张，使尿液通过尿道排出体外。<ref name=":6" />

当膀胱内贮尿量达到300－400毫升时，一些[[受体_(生物化学)|受体]]会被激活，从而使机体产生排尿冲动。<ref name=":6" />随着尿液的累积，膀胱襞变平，膀胱壁随其伸展而变薄，使得膀胱在储存更多尿液的情况下内部压力不发生明显上升。<ref>{{cite book|author=Marieb, Mallatt|title=Human Anatomy|year=2016|url=https://archive.org/details/humananatomyphys0000mari_k5b8|edition=5th|publisher=Pearson International|chapter=23|page=[https://archive.org/details/humananatomyphys0000mari_k5b8/page/700 700]}}</ref>

当膀胱扩张时，膀胱中的{{Translink|en|Stretch receptors|牵张感受器}}向副交感神经发出信号，激活逼尿肌中的[[蕈毒鹼型乙醯膽鹼受體|M受体]]，促进逼尿肌收缩、尿道括约肌舒张，故可促进排尿。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Muscarinic receptor subtypes in the lower urinary tract|first1=D|last2=Tobin|first2=G|date=2009|journal=Pharmacology|issue=5|doi=10.1159/000209255|volume=83|pages=259–69|pmid=19295256|last1=Giglio|doi-access=free}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|edition=9 ban|chapter=Sheng li xue = Physiology|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/1178824538|publisher=Ren min wei sheng chu ban she|date=2018|location=Beijing|isbn=978-7-117-26659-8|oclc=1178824538|last=Wang,Tinghuai|last2=王庭槐|title=生理学|access-date=2021-07-20|archive-date=2021-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210720043910/https://www.worldcat.org/title/sheng-li-xue-physiology/oclc/1178824538|dead-url=no}}</ref>逼尿肌的收缩主要由[[蕈毒鹼型乙醯膽鹼受體#M3受體|M<sub>3</sub>受体]]介导。逼尿肌中分布密度更高的[[蕈毒鹼型乙醯膽鹼受體#M2受體|M<sub>2</sub>受体]]发挥次要作用。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Muscarinic receptor subtypes of the bladder and gastrointestinal tract|first1=T|last2=Chess-Williams|first2=R|date=December 2004|journal=Journal of Smooth Muscle Research = Nihon Heikatsukin Gakkai Kikanshi|issue=6|doi=10.1540/jsmr.40.237|volume=40|pages=237–47|pmid=15725706|last1=Uchiyama|doi-access=free}}</ref>

膀胱的松弛主要依靠[[單磷酸腺苷|腺苷酸]]环化酶[[环腺苷酸|cAMP]]通路，由[[肾上腺素受体|肾上腺素受体]]β3激活。肾上腺素受体β2也存在于逼尿肌中且数目更多，但其舒张逼尿肌的功能较弱。<ref name=":9" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Adrenoceptor Function and Expression in Bladder Urothelium and Lamina Propria|first1=Christian|last2=Tajouri|first2=Lotti|journal=Urology|issue=1|doi=10.1016/j.urology.2012.09.011|year=2013|volume=81|pages=211.e1–211.e7|pmid=23200975|last3=Chess-Williams|first3=Russ|last1=Moro}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Neurophysiology of Stress Urinary Incontinence|first1=M. B.|last2=Yoshimura|first2=N.|journal=Rev. Urol.|year=2004|volume=6 Suppl 3|pages=S19–28|pmc=1472861|pmid=16985861|last1=Chancellor}}</ref>

== 临床意义 ==

=== 感染与炎症 ===
{{主条目|膀胱炎}}
[[File:Schistosomiaisis_Bladder_Calcifications.png|缩略图]]
当[[泌尿道感染|泌尿道感染]]波及膀胱时将会引发膀胱炎。由于成年女性尿道较短，这种疾病更多见于女性。男童与患[[良性前列腺增生症|前列腺肥大]]、[[尿瀦留|尿潴留]]的老年人亦常患此病。其他危险因素包括：[[前列腺癌|前列腺癌]]或膀胱输尿管反流引起的尿道阻塞或狭窄、使用[[导尿管|导尿管]]、导致排尿困难的神经系统疾病。膀胱的感染可引起下腹部疼痛（指耻骨联合以上部位常发于排尿前后的疼痛），也会导致尿频与尿急。感染通常由细菌引起，最常见者是[[大腸桿菌|大肠杆菌]]。<ref name=":12" />

当怀疑泌尿道感染时，医生可能要求患者提供尿液样本。通过检查尿液中的[[白血球|白细胞]]或[[硝酸盐|硝酸盐]]含量可判断感染是否发生。尿液样本也可能用于微生物培养和{{Translink|en|antibiotic sensitivities|药物敏感性}}评估。进一步检查可能包括通过[[电解质|电解质]]、[[肌酸酐|肌酐]]含量评估肾脏功能、通过[[超聲波|超声波]]检查肾道是否存在阻塞或狭窄、通过{{Translink|en|digital rectal examination|直肠指诊}}检查前列腺是否肥大。<ref name=":12" />

通常使用口服[[抗细菌药|抗生素]]来治疗膀胱炎。感染严重者可能需要[[靜脈注射|静脉注射]]抗生素治疗。<ref name=":12">{{cite book|title=Davidson's principles and practice of medicine|last1=Ralston|first1=Stuart H.|last2=Penman|first2=Ian D.|last3=Strachan|first3=Mark W.|last4=Hobson|first4=Richard P. (eds.)|date=2018|publisher=Elsevier|isbn=978-0-7020-7028-0|edition=23rd}}</ref>

=== 尿频、尿失禁与尿潴留 ===
尿频即每天小便次数超过八次。<ref>{{cite web|title=Overactive Bladder|url=https://www.cornellurology.com/clinical-conditions/female-urology-urogynecology/overactive-bladder|access-date=2013-08-21|publisher=Cornell Medical College|archive-date=2016-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160602223527/https://www.cornellurology.com/clinical-conditions/female-urology-urogynecology/overactive-bladder/|dead-url=no}}</ref>产尿过多、膀胱容量小或膀胱排空不完全可能导致尿频。患前列腺肥大的男性常常尿频。尿频可能会导致失禁。排尿频率和尿量在正常情况下符合[[昼夜节律|昼夜节律]]，但膀胱的过度活动会干扰这一节律。[[尿路動力學|尿路动力学]]可以用于解释这一症状。膀胱活动不足是神经性膀胱功能异常的主要症状，会导致排尿困难。夜间的尿频则可能提示膀胱结石。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Involvement of urinary bladder Connexin43 and the circadian clock in coordination of diurnal micturition rhythm|last=Negoro|first=Hiromitsu|journal=Nature Communications|doi=10.1038/ncomms1812|year=2012|volume=3|page=809|bibcode=2012NatCo...3..809N|pmc=3541943|pmid=22549838}}</ref>

=== 癌症 ===
{{主条目|膀胱癌}}
[[File:Bladder_Cancer.jpg|缩略图]]
膀胱癌常是尿路上皮细胞癌，多见于年龄超过40岁的男性，危险因素包括[[吸菸|吸烟]]、接触含[[芳香胺|芳香胺]]和[[醛|醛]]类物质的[[染料|染料]]等。癌症发生时，患者最常见的症状是[[血尿|血尿]]。除晚期癌症外，患者的[[体格检查|体格检查]]可能正常。若尿道内壁细胞因结石或[[血吸虫病|血吸虫病]]等慢性炎症而发生变化，亦可有鳞状细胞癌出现。<ref name=":13" />

检查通常包括尿液样本恶性细胞镜检，即[[细胞生物学|细胞学]]检查，以及[[X射线计算机断层成像|CT]]或超声波尿路造影等[[醫學影像|影像学]]检查。[[膀胱镜|膀胱镜]]可查看病变并进行[[活體組織切片|组织活检]]。其他身体部位的CT扫描可寻找转移性癌变。<ref name=":13" />

膀胱癌治疗方法取决于[[癌症分期|癌症分期]]。仅存在于膀胱的肿瘤可以通过膀胱镜手术切除并注射[[丝裂霉素|丝裂霉素]]治疗。高度恶性的肿瘤可在膀胱壁内注射[[卡介苗|卡介苗]]治疗，效果不明显时需手术切除。侵犯膀胱壁的癌症可以通过{{Translink|en|Cystectomy#Radical_cystectomy|根治性膀胱切除术}}进行治疗，这一手术需将输尿管连接至体外的{{Translink|en|stoma bag|造口袋}}。膀胱癌的[[预后|预后]]因癌症分期和[[腫瘤分級|分级]]而有显著差异，通常不侵犯膀胱壁的乳头状瘤预后较好。<ref name=":13">{{cite book|title=Davidson's principles and practice of medicine|last1=Ralston|first1=Stuart H.|last2=Penman|first2=Ian D.|last3=Strachan|first3=Mark W.|last4=Hobson|first4=Richard P. (eds.)|date=2018|publisher=Elsevier|isbn=978-0-7020-7028-0|edition=23rd|pages=435–6|section=Urothelial tumours}}</ref>

=== 医学检查 ===
{{更多信息|膀胱镜}}
用于检查膀胱的医学检查手段包括[[血液检查|血液检查]]、[[尿液分析|尿液检查]]等。例如，白细胞数目上升可能提示膀胱炎症。亦可采取CT、[[核磁共振成像|MRI]]或超声波等方式对膀胱进行影像学检查。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Urinary Tract Imaging {{!}} NIDDK|url=https://www.niddk.nih.gov/health-information/diagnostic-tests/urinary-tract-imaging|access-date=2021-07-20|work=National Institute of Diabetes and Digestive and Kidney Diseases|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410030103/https://www.niddk.nih.gov/health-information/diagnostic-tests/urinary-tract-imaging|dead-url=no}}</ref>膀胱镜可用于对膀胱壁的直接观察、组织活检。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Cystoscopy and Ureteroscopy - Doctors Lounge(TM)|url=https://www.doctorslounge.com/urology/procedures/cystoscopy.htm|access-date=2021-07-20|work=www.doctorslounge.com|archive-date=2019-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190126220720/https://www.doctorslounge.com/urology/procedures/cystoscopy.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>尿路动力学检查则有助于医生了解患病原因与机理。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Contemporary diagnosis of lower urinary tract dysfunction|author=Rosier P|journal=F1000Res|doi=10.12688/f1000research.16120.1|year=2019|volume=8|pages=644|pmc=6509958|pmid=31119030}}</ref>

== 其他动物 ==
[[File:Blasenstein_OP_Situs.jpg|缩略图]]

=== 哺乳动物 ===
所有[[哺乳动物|哺乳动物]]都拥有膀胱。膀胱的发育始于胚胎泄殖腔。在绝大多数情况下，泄殖腔最终会分化为腹侧的尿生殖窦和背侧的原始直肠。无此分化现象的哺乳动物仅有[[鸭嘴兽|鸭嘴兽]]和[[针鼹|针鼹]]，这两种动物成年期仍保留有泄殖腔。<ref name=":10">{{cite book|url=https://archive.org/stream/chordates00rand/#page/276/mode/1up/search/bladder|title=The Chordates|date=1950|publisher=Balkiston|author=Herbert W. Rand}}</ref>

[[鯨豚類|鲸目]]动物（如[[鯨|鲸鱼]]和[[海豚|海豚]]）的膀胱比陆地哺乳动物的膀胱小得多。<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=TNAIBwAAQBAJ&pg=PR35|title=The Works of John Hunter, F.R.S.|date=2015-03-26|publisher=Cambridge University|isbn=978-1-108-07960-0|page=35|author=John Hunter|access-date=2021-07-19|archive-date=2021-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415042648/https://books.google.com/books?id=TNAIBwAAQBAJ&pg=PR35|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 爬行动物 ===
[[爬行动物|爬行动物]]的排泄物均流入泄殖腔。一些爬行动物泄殖腔的中腹壁在膀胱处有开口。这一结构存在于所有的[[海龟|海龟]]、[[陸龜|陆龟]]以及大多数[[蜥蜴|蜥蜴]]体内，但[[巨蜥|巨蜥]]体内无此结构。[[蛇|蛇]]和[[鳄鱼|鳄鱼]]体内亦不存在此结构。<ref name=":10" />{{Rp|474}}

许多海龟、陆龟和蜥蜴拥有占体重比较高的膀胱。[[查尔斯·达尔文|查尔斯 · 达尔文]]指出，[[加拉帕戈斯象龜|加拉帕戈斯象龟]]的膀胱可以重达体重的20%。<ref name="auto">{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=U0D3BwAAQBAJ&pg=PA143|title=Endocrines and Osmoregulation: A Comparative Account in Vertebrates|date=2013-03-14|publisher=Springer Science & Business Media|isbn=978-3-662-05014-9|author=P.J. Bentley|access-date=2021-07-19|archive-date=2021-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210531050224/https://books.google.com/books?id=U0D3BwAAQBAJ&pg=PA143|dead-url=no}}</ref>这种结构是适应偏远岛屿和缺水[[沙漠|沙漠]]等环境的结果。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Reptile Basics: Clinical Anatomy 101|author=|url=http://www.ivis.org/proceedings/navc/2006/SAE/600.pdf?LA=1|last=Paré|first=Jean|date=2006-01-11|journal=Proceedings of the North American Veterinary Conference|volume=20|pages=1657–1660|access-date=2021-07-19|archive-date=2019-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608150637/http://www.ivis.org/proceedings/navc/2006/SAE/600.pdf?LA=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>生活在沙漠中的爬行动物拥有巨大的膀胱，可以长期储水，有助于其机体[[滲透壓|渗透压]]的调节。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The urinary bladder as a physiological reservoir that moderates dehydration in a large desert lizard, the Gila monster Heloderma suspectum|first1=Jon R.|last2=DeNardo|first2=Dale F.|date=2007-04-15|journal=Journal of Experimental Biology|issue=8|doi=10.1242/jeb.003061|volume=210|pages=1472–1480|language=en|issn=0022-0949|pmid=17401130|last1=Davis|doi-access=free}}</ref>

龟有两个或两个以上的副膀胱，位于膀胱颈侧和耻骨背侧，占据一大部分体腔。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Urogenital System|author=|url=http://www.ivis.org/advances/wyneken/16.pdf?LA|first1=Jeanette|last2=Witherington|first2=Dawn|date=2015-02|journal=Anatomy of Sea Turtles|volume=1|pages=153–165|last1=Wyneken|access-date=2021-07-19|archive-date=2019-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608150657/http://www.ivis.org/advances/wyneken/16.pdf?LA|dead-url=no}}</ref>它们的膀胱通常分为左右两部。右侧部分位于肝脏下方，这样可以避免大结石留于该侧。<ref>{{Cite book|title=Reptile Medicine and Surgery|last1=Divers|first1=Stephen J.|last2=Mader|first2=Douglas R.|publisher=Elsevier Health Sciences|year=2005|isbn=9781416064770|location=Amsterdam|pages=481, 597}}</ref>

=== 两栖动物 ===
大多数水栖和半水栖[[两栖动物|两栖动物]]都拥有膜性的皮肤，允许它们直接通过皮肤吸收水分。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Comparative study of the effects of different diuretics on the permeability properties of the toad bladder|first1=Shigeharu|last2=Shirai|first2=Dairoku|journal=Comparative Biochemistry and Physiology Part C: Comparative Pharmacology|issue=2|doi=10.1016/0306-4492(76)90063-0|year=1976|volume=53|pages=115–119|language=en|pmid=5237|last3=Yuasa|first3=Shigekazu|last4=Kimura|first4=Genjiro|last5=Orita|first5=Yoshimasa|last6=Abe|first6=Hiroshi|last1=Urakabe}}</ref>一些半水栖动物也有类似的可渗透膀胱膜。因此，他们的尿液排出率往往很高，以抵消这种高水分摄入，同时尿液中含盐量很低。膀胱有助于这些动物保留盐分。有些水生两栖动物，如[[爪蟾屬|爪蟾]]，可停止重吸收水以避免摄入过多水分。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Molecular and cellular characterization of urinary bladder-type aquaporin in Xenopus laevis|first1=Yuki|last2=Katayama|first2=Izumi|journal=General and Comparative Endocrinology|doi=10.1016/j.ygcen.2014.09.001|year=2015|volume=222|pages=11–19|pmid=25220852|last3=Nakakura|first3=Takashi|last4=Ogushi|first4=Yuji|last5=Okada|first5=Reiko|last6=Tanaka|first6=Shigeyasu|last7=Suzuki|first7=Masakazu|last1=Shibata}}</ref>对于陆栖两栖动物，脱水会导致尿量减少。<ref name=":11">{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Gay9N_ry79kC&pg=PA184|title=Herpetology: An Introductory Biology of Amphibians and Reptiles|date=2013-03-25|publisher=Academic|isbn=978-0-12-386920-3|author1=Laurie J. Vitt|author2=Janalee P. Caldwell|page=184|access-date=2021-07-19|archive-date=2021-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415032419/https://books.google.com/books?id=Gay9N_ry79kC&pg=PA184|dead-url=no}}</ref>

两栖动物的膀胱通常高度膨胀，一些陆栖[[蛙類|蛙类]]和[[蝾螈科|蝾螈]]的膀胱可能占其体重的20%至50%。<ref name=":11" />

=== 鱼类 ===
尽管大多数[[硬骨魚類|硬骨鱼类]]有帮助消除体内[[氨|氨]]的[[鳃|鳃]]，它们仍拥有一个用于储存废液的膀胱。硬骨鱼的膀胱可渗透水分，其中[[咸水|咸水]]鱼类的膀胱渗透功能更强。<ref name="auto"/>{{rp|219}}大多数鱼还拥有[[鰾|鳔]]，但其除膜性质类似外与膀胱无关。[[泥鳅|泥鳅]]、[[沙丁魚|沙丁鱼]]和[[鯡魚|鲱鱼]]是少数几种膀胱发育不良的鱼类。无鳔的鱼类膀胱体积最大，位置通常位于[[输卵管|输卵管]]前、直肠后。<ref>{{Cite book|title=Lectures on the comparative anatomy and physiology of the invertebrate animals|last=Owen|first=Richard|publisher=Longman, Brown, Green, and Longmans|year=1843|location=London|pages=283–284|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=pNpPpKj4_tgC|access-date=2021-07-19|archive-date=2021-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415032316/https://books.google.com/books?id=pNpPpKj4_tgC|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 鸟类 ===

几乎所有的[[鸟|鸟类]]都没有膀胱。<ref>{{cite book|author=Cornell University. Laboratory of Ornithology|title=Handbook of Bird Biology|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=OGyQDAAAQBAJ&q=bird+urinary+bladder|date=2016-11-19|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|isbn=978-1-118-29105-4|access-date=2021-07-19|archive-date=2021-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415042747/https://books.google.com/books?id=OGyQDAAAQBAJ&q=bird+urinary+bladder|dead-url=no}}</ref>鸟类的输尿管开口于泄殖腔，泄殖腔充当储存尿液、粪便和卵的容器。<ref>{{cite book|url=https://archive.org/details/in.ernet.dli.2015.45180|title=The English Cyclopaedia: A New Dictionary of Universal Knowledge|publisher=Bradbury and Evans|year=1854|page=[https://archive.org/details/in.ernet.dli.2015.45180/page/n71 136]|author=Charles Knight}}</ref>

=== 甲壳动物 ===
与脊椎动物的膀胱不同，[[甲殼亞門|甲壳动物]]的膀胱既储存尿液，也会改变尿液成分。膀胱由两组侧叶和中央叶组成。中央叶靠近消化器官，侧叶沿其体腔的前部和两侧延伸。其膀胱由薄[[上皮細胞|上皮细胞]]构成。<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=trazj_5gCSQC&pg=PA47|title=Nonmammalian animal models for biomedical research|date=1989|publisher=CRC Press|others=Woodhead, Avril D.|isbn=0-8493-4763-7|location=Boca Raton, Fla.|pages=51–52|oclc=18816053|access-date=2021-07-19|archive-date=2021-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415032304/https://books.google.com/books?id=trazj_5gCSQC&pg=PA47|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 文化 ==
[[File:Pieter_Brueghel_the_Elder_-_Kinderspielbild_-_Schweinsblase.png|缩略图]]画作中持猪膀胱的儿童]]
人类通过屠宰动物获取的膀胱有许多用途。例如，膀胱是最早用于储存和运输液体、[[乾酪|奶酪]]甚至文件的容器之一。欧洲的一些传统[[肉腸|香肠]]和肉菜会使用动物膀胱包裹。在[[中世纪|中世纪]]，人们有时会用覆盖着猪膀胱的木框替代玻璃窗。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Fenster - regionalgeschichte.net|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150318054759/http://www.regionalgeschichte.net/index.php?id=1084|access-date=2021-07-19|date=2015-03-18|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>

儿童会把晒干或风干的膀胱当作玩具。例如，英国国王[[亨利八世|亨利八世]]喜欢用猪膀胱作为足球<ref>{{Cite web|title=Kicken bei Hofe|url=https://www.stern.de/sport/fussball/fussballgeschichte-kicken-bei-hofe-3075512.html|access-date=2021-07-19|work=stern.de|language=de|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204074343/https://www.stern.de/sport/fussball/fussballgeschichte-kicken-bei-hofe-3075512.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、农村的儿童会将风干的猪膀胱当作早期的气球。<ref>{{Cite web|title=gezetera online PRINT|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070807110200/http://www.gezetera.ch/gezetera_print/ausgabe.php3?ID=330|access-date=2021-07-19|date=2007-08-07|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>1687年的一个宴会食谱上曾介绍过这样的食品：在一个猪膀胱内装入约25个鸡蛋黄，然后将其浸入沸水中使蛋黄变成固体；将所得球体放置在更大的膀胱中，囊中装满[[蛋白|蛋清]]；再次浸入沸水中使蛋清凝固，制成“巨蛋”。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Italienische Rezepte: Venetien (Veneto)|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110714144640/http://www.g26.ch/italien_rezepte_regionen_veneto.html|access-date=2021-07-19|date=2011-07-14|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>

在古代中国，[[蹴鞠|蹴鞠]]运动一度较为流行。[[唐朝|唐代]]曾出现过用充气动物膀胱作为鞠球内胆的制作工艺，促进了这一运动的发展。<ref>{{Cite web|title=长安旧时蹴鞠热 一球传袭动乾坤 蹴鞠与足球：古今相连精彩依旧-国际在线|url=http://sn.cri.cn/n/20210422/16dc9fd3-c3b9-5deb-3a9e-9ce689b8c61a.html|access-date=2021-07-20|author=张杨|date=2021-04-22|coauthors=郝钟毓, 黄艳|work=sn.cri.cn|publisher=西安新闻网|archive-date=2021-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210720043452/http://sn.cri.cn/n/20210422/16dc9fd3-c3b9-5deb-3a9e-9ce689b8c61a.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=中国古代蹴鞠|author=崔乐泉|url=https://www.ixueshu.com/document/1ac2992c2edbc0aca828c4e4ce9bda27318947a18e7f9386.html|journal=管子学刊|issue=3|doi=10.3969/j.issn.1002-3828.2004.03.009|year=2004|page=43-51|access-date=2021-07-20|archive-date=2021-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210720043550/https://www.ixueshu.com/document/1ac2992c2edbc0aca828c4e4ce9bda27318947a18e7f9386.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

由于丹麦宫廷礼仪禁止客人在皇帝面前起立，天文学家[[第谷·布拉赫|第谷·布拉赫]]曾在1601年10月13日皇帝举办的宴会上膀胱破裂。他在十天后去世，原因可能为膀胱感染。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Mercury poisoning ruled out as cause of Tycho Brahe's death|url=https://projekter.au.dk/en/tycho-brahe/pressreleases/mercury-poisoning-ruled-out-as-cause-of-tycho-brahes-death/|access-date=2021-07-19|last=463237@au.dk|work=projekter.au.dk|language=en|archive-date=2021-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210630065503/https://projekter.au.dk/en/tycho-brahe/pressreleases/mercury-poisoning-ruled-out-as-cause-of-tycho-brahes-death/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

19世纪前，因饮食引起的膀胱结石是一种常见病。由于[[希波克拉底誓詞|希波克拉底誓言]]禁止医生对其进行治疗，因此出现了独立的碎石师职业。其中最著名的代表是{{Translink|en|Johann Andreas Eisenbarth|约翰·安德烈亚斯·艾森巴特}}。<ref>Eike Pies: <nowiki>''</nowiki>Eisenbarth. Das Ende einer Legende.<nowiki>''</nowiki> 2004, S. 44.</ref>

[[爱斯基摩人|爱斯基摩人]]认为膀胱是灵魂所在之处。因此，他们全年都要从被猎杀的海豹身上收集膀胱。在每年一次的“膀胱节”上，人们装饰膀胱后将它们放入大海，使得海洋动物以此为养分繁衍，以便来年捕猎。<ref>Hans Himmelheber: <nowiki>''</nowiki>Eskimokünstler.<nowiki>''</nowiki> Strecker & Schröder, Stuttgart 1938; Röth, Eisenach 1953.</ref>

